# MeowKit
.env
.env.local
# Memory dir: machine-local files are ignored; topic files (team learnings) are excepted.
# NOTE: To un-ignore files inside an ignored directory, we must not ignore the directory itself.
# Instead we ignore individual machine-local files and keep topic files trackable.
.claude/memory/cost-log.json
.claude/memory/conversation-summary.md
.claude/memory/trace-log.jsonl
.claude/memory/quick-notes.md
.claude/memory/last-model-id.txt
.claude/memory/.*.lock
# Topic files below are intentionally NOT ignored — they are team learnings committed to repo.
.claude/cache/
.claude/logs/
.claude/metadata.json
.claude/session-state/
.claude/packs/
release-manifest.json

